                                                                                                                                Indicators and status

                                                                                                                                Progress bar

                                                                                                                                Stable

                                                                                                                                A progress bar is a graphical representation of progress over time. It's typically used to show the progress of an ongoing process, like content loading, file uploading, or the completion of steps for an Uber Eats order.
